<page-sections>
  <page-section>
    {{> "portfolio-header" }}
		<div class="stage type-full" style="background-color: rgb(246,245,243)">
			<img class="full-width image" src="/media/swift-stage.jpg" alt="swift / we are fast" />
    </div>
  </page-section>
  <page-section centered maxwidth="1000px">
    <h3 class="o-headline--portfolio u-margin-top-xl">swift / we are fast</h3>
  </page-section>
  <page-section class="c-section-portfolio-intro" centered maxwidth="1000px">
    <div class="o-project-info o-project-section-container">
      <div class="o-project-info__item">
        <h4 class="o-project-info__title">Industry</h4>
        <div class="o-project-info__description">Travel</div>
      </div>
      <div class="o-project-info__item">
        <h4 class="o-project-info__title">Created</h4>
        <div class="o-project-info__description">2011</div>
      </div>
      <div class="o-project-info__item">
        <h4 class="o-project-info__title">Objective</h4>
        <p class="o-project-info__intro">Branding for a modern airline which differentiates itself by speed instead of entering the endless pricing battle.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </page-section>
  <page-section centered maxwidth="1000px">
    <div class="o-raster o-project-section-container">
      <div class="o-copy--big o-column--md-10 o-column--sm-16 u-margin-bottom-xl">
        <p>swift is an airline corporate identity focusing on the corporate values comfort, trust and speed.</p><p>The primary color yellow visualises speed and is mainly used in communication and marketing, while the dark green stands for comfort and calmness and is mainly used inside the airplanes & lounge areas.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </page-section>
  <page-section centered maxwidth="1000px">
    <div class="o-raster o-project-section-container">
      <h3 class="o-headline--portfolio u-margin-top-xl o-column--md-16">Swift Logo Design</h3>
      <div class="o-column--md-16">
        <img src="/media/swift-logo.jpg" alt="Swift logo design" />
      </div>
      <div class="o-column--md-8 o-column--sm-16 u-margin-top-md">
        <img src="/media/swift-logo-construction.jpg" alt="Swift logo constrcution" class="u-width-full u-padding-right-sm" />
      </div>
      <div class="o-column--md-8 o-column--sm-16 u-margin-top-md">
        <img src="/media/swift-logo-lockup.jpg" alt="Swift logo lockup" class="u-width-full u-padding-left-sm" />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="o-raster o-project-section-container u-margin-top-lg">
      <div class="o-column--sm-16 o-column--md-8 ">
        <p class="o-copy--big u-padding-right-sm">It took about 100 different variations of 6 names to find the one that was just right, a reduced Logotype that is bend to the right to give a feeling of movement and a rough resemblence of the shape of an airplane.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="o-column--sm-16 o-column--md-8">
  		  <p class="o-copy--big u-padding-left-sm">The logo did not only have to be trustworthy, but needed to fit wiht the target audience of mainly traveling businessmen.</p>
  		</div>
  		<div class="o-column--offset-sm-0 o-column--offset-md-3 o-column--md-10 o-column--sm-16 u-margin-top-lg">
  		  <img src="/media/swift-logo-sketches.jpg" alt="Swift logo Ideas" class="u-width-full" />
  		</div>
    </div>
  </page-section>
  <page-section centered maxwidth="1000px">
    <div class="o-raster u-margin-top-xl o-project-section-container">
      <h3 class="o-headline--portfolio u-margin-top-xl o-column--md-16">Corporate Colors & Patterns</h3>
      <div class="o-column--md-16">
		    <img src="/media/swift-colors.jpg" alt="Corporate Colors" class="u-width-full" />
      </div>
      <div class="o-column--md-8 o-column--sm-16 u-margin-top-md">
        <img src="/media/swift-pattern_01.jpg" alt="Corporate Patterns" class="u-width-full u-padding-right-sm" />
      </div>
      <div class="o-column--md-8 o-column--sm-16 u-margin-top-md">
        <img src="/media/swift-pattern_02.jpg" alt="Corporate Patterns" class="u-width-full u-padding-left-sm" />
      </div>
		</div>
  </page-section>
  <page-section centered maxwidth="1000px">
    <div class="o-raster u-margin-top-xl o-project-section-container">
      <h3 class="o-headline--portfolio u-margin-top-xl o-column--md-16">Stationeries</h3>
      <div class="o-column--md-16">
		    <img src="/media/swift-stationeries.jpg" alt="Stationeries in Corporate Design" class="u-width-full" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </page-section>
  <page-section centered maxwidth="1000px">
    <div class="o-raster u-margin-top-xl o-project-section-container">
      <h3 class="o-headline--portfolio u-margin-top-xl o-column--md-16">Architecture & Vehicles</h3>
      <div class="o-column--md-8 o-column--sm-16 u-margin-top-md">
        <img src="/media/swift-car.jpg" alt="vehicle with corporate colors & elements" class="u-width-full u-padding-right-sm" />
      </div>
      <div class="o-column--md-8 o-column--sm-16 u-margin-top-md">
        <img src="/media/swift-flags.jpg" alt="Swift flag design" class="u-width-full u-padding-left-sm" />
      </div>
      <div class="o-column--md-8 o-column--sm-16 u-margin-top-md">
        <img src="/media/swift-lounge.jpg" alt="swift passanger lounge" class="u-width-full u-padding-right-sm" />
      </div>
      <div class="o-column--md-8 o-column--sm-16 u-margin-top-md">
        <img src="/media/swift-checkin.jpg" alt="swift help desk" class="u-width-full u-padding-left-sm" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </page-section>
  <page-section centered maxwidth="1000px">
    <div class="u-width-full u-padding-bottom-xl o-project-section-container">
      <a class="o-button o-button--floating o-button--primary u-margin-top-xl u-margin-bottom-xl" href="/portfolio">&larr; return to overview</a>
    </div>
  </page-section>
</page-sections>
